General Information

Gluten Free, Low Carb, high protein mini protein bar

Warnings

Contains milk and soy.

Ingredients

Protein Blend 33% (Soy Protein Isolate, Whey Protein Isolate, Whey Protein Concentrate, Calcium Caseinate, Soy Protein Nuggets), No Added Sugar Protein White Chocolate 18% (Maltitol, Cocoa Butter 33%, Soy Protein Isolate, Milk Solids 10%, Emulsifiers (Soy Lecithin, 476), Citric Acid), Polydextrose, Maltitol, Sorbitol, Caramel Paste 8% (Invert Sugar, Humectants (Sorbitol, Glycerol), Concentrated Pear Puree, Polydextrose, Sunflower Oil, Citrus Fibre, Natural Colours (Caramel I, Titanium Dioxide), Gelling Agent (Pectin), Firming Agent (Calcium Lactate), Natural Flavour), Humectant (Glycerol), Sugar Free Caramel Chips 3%, Sunflower Oil, Treacle, Flavour, Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Salt, Sweetener (Steviol Glycosides), Antioxidant (Vitamin E). White protein chocolate contains 10% milk solids minimum.
